metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Azul ft Reyli is significantly more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Azul ft Reyli has sections analyzed in the following keys: G♯ Minor,  and F♯ Mixolydian.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: I love this song because it mixes G# Aeolian with F# Mixolydian (both belonging to B Ionian). Its progression reminds me of "Early Winter" by Gwen Stefani.
